data.description: Welcome home to this updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single story home. As you enter the foyer, you will find a beautiful kitchen and open dining and living room. Cozy up by fire on chilly nights enjoying the company of your family and friends. The primary bedroom has a beautiful en suite bath complete with a separate garden tub and shower which is the perfect oasis after a long day. The large backyard sits on this corner lot and is the perfect spot to host summer BBQs and gatherings. Don’t miss the chance to make this inviting residence your holiday haven.
